verses.text:
He suffered and died at Gethsemane, the lot was that light, shame;
He suffered and died at Gethsemane, in agony of pain;
He suffered and died at Gethsemane, that their souls might be saved;
He suffered and died at Gethsemane, for sins our souls have made.

